- 透明设置:  

```rust
let win = ApplicationWindow::builder()
    .application(app)
    .title("My Gtk App")
    .opacity(0.8)         // 窗口不透明度, 越低越透明, 越高越不透明
    .build();
```

- 默认高宽:

```rust
